@startuml
title UC-21 Admin Approve Garage - Activity Diagram

|Garage Owner|
start
:Submit Garage Registration;

|System|
:Store Registration as Pending;

|Admin|
:Open Pending Garage Applications;
:Review Business Information;
:Verify Documents and Registration Details;

while (Information Complete?) is (No)

  :Request Additional Information;

  |System|
  :Notify Garage Owner;

  |Garage Owner|
  :Submit Missing Information;

  |Admin|
  :Review Updated Information;

endwhile (Yes)

if (Registration Valid?) then (Yes)

  :Approve Garage;

  |System|
  :Update Garage Status to Approved;
  :Make Garage Visible to Customers;
  :Send Approval Notification to Garage Owner;

else (No)

  :Reject Application;

  |System|
  :Send Rejection Notification to Garage Owner;

endif

stop

@enduml